8270286Di2015UniqueSeparatorMeasure
8270286Di2015UniqueSeparatore.Measure(availableSize)
8270286Di2015UniqueSeparatorprotected override Size MeasureOverride(Size availableSize)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    Size requiredSize = new Size();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    var itemAvailableSize = new Size(availableSize.Width, availableSize.Height / InternalChildren.Count);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    foreach (UIElement e in InternalChildren)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        e.Measure(itemAvailableSize);Di2015NewLine        requiredSize.Height += e.DesiredSize.Height;Di2015NewLine        requiredSize.Width = Math.Max(requiredSize.Width, e.DesiredSize.Width);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return new Size(Di2015NewLine        Math.Min(availableSize.Width, requiredSize.Width),Di2015NewLine        Math.Min(availableSize.Height, requiredSize.Height));Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
8270286Di2015UniqueSeparatoravailableSize
8270286Di2015UniqueSeparatordouble.PositiveInfinity

8270286Di2015UniqueSeparatorprotected override Size MeasureOverride(Size availableSize)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    var requiredSize = new Size();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    double allItemsHeight = 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    foreach (UIElement e in InternalChildren)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        e.Measure(new Size(availableSize.Width, double.PositiveInfinity));Di2015NewLine        allItemsHeight += e.DesiredSize.Height;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    double scale = 1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (allItemsHeight > availableSize.Height)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        scale = availableSize.Height / allItemsHeight;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    foreach (UIElement e in InternalChildren)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        double height = e.DesiredSize.Height * scale;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        e.Measure(new Size(availableSize.Width, height));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        requiredSize.Height += e.DesiredSize.Height;Di2015NewLine        requiredSize.Width = Math.Max(requiredSize.Width, e.DesiredSize.Width);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return new Size(Di2015NewLine        Math.Min(availableSize.Width, requiredSize.Width),Di2015NewLine        Math.Min(availableSize.Height, requiredSize.Height));Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8271632Di2015UniqueSeparator    public static IQueryable<T> Where<T, TProperty>(this IQueryable<T> source,Di2015NewLine        Expression<Func<T, TProperty>> propertySelector,Di2015NewLine        Expression<Func<TProperty, bool>> predicate)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        MemberExpression member = propertySelector.Body as MemberExpression;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (member == null)Di2015NewLine            throw new ArgumentException("Must be a property selector", "propertySelector");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        string propertyName = member.Member.Name;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // The input typeDi2015NewLine        ParameterExpression propertyParameter = Expression.Parameter(typeof(T));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // The property on that typeDi2015NewLine        MemberExpression itemProperty = Expression.Property(propertyParameter, propertyName);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Invoke the specified predicate with the property from the input typeDi2015NewLine        InvocationExpression invokeExpression = Expression.Invoke(predicate, itemProperty);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // The lambda expression for use with LinqDi2015NewLine        Expression<Func<T, bool>> finalExpression = Expression.Lambda<Func<T, bool>>(invokeExpression, propertyParameter);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return source.Where(finalExpression);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

8281486Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static TSource MaxBy<TSource, TKey>(this IEnumerable<TSource> source,Di2015NewLine    Func<TSource, TKey> selector, IComparer<TKey> comparer)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    using (IEnumerator<TSource> sourceIterator = source.GetEnumerator())Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        if (!sourceIterator.MoveNext())Di2015NewLine            throw new InvalidOperationException("Sequence was empty");Di2015NewLine        TSource max = sourceIterator.Current;Di2015NewLine        TKey maxKey = selector(max);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        while (sourceIterator.MoveNext())Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            TSource candidate = sourceIterator.Current;Di2015NewLine            TKey candidateProjected = selector(candidate);Di2015NewLine            if (comparer.Compare(candidateProjected, maxKey) > 0)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                max = candidate;Di2015NewLine                maxKey = candidateProjected;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return max;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8284251Di2015UniqueSeparator    private static int[] ResizeArray(int[] oldArray, int newSize)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int oldSize = oldArray.Length;Di2015NewLine        int rectangle = newSize * oldSize;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var upsampled = Enumerable.Range(0, rectangle).Select(k => oldArray[k / newSize]).ToArray();Di2015NewLine        var downSampled = Enumerable.Range(0, newSize).Select(j => Enumerable.Range(0, oldSize-1).Select(i => upsampled[j * oldSize + i])).Select(g => g.Average());Di2015NewLine        return downSampled.Select(i => (int)i).ToArray();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

8285867Di2015UniqueSeparator/// <summary>  Di2015NewLine/// Programatically registers a <see cref="SoapExtension"/> at runtime with the specified  Di2015NewLine/// <see cref="SoapExtensionTypeElement.Priority"/> and <see cref="SoapExtensionTypeElement.Group"/> settings.  Di2015NewLine/// </summary>  Di2015NewLine/// <param name="type">The <see cref="Type"/> of the <see cref="SoapExtension"/> to register.</param>  Di2015NewLine/// <param name="priority">  Di2015NewLine/// A value that indicates the relative order in which this SOAP extension runs when multiple SOAP extensions are  Di2015NewLine/// specified. Within each group the priority attribute distinguishes the overall relative priority of the SOAP   Di2015NewLine/// extension. A lower priority number indicates a higher priority for the SOAP extension. The lowest possible   Di2015NewLine/// value for the priority attribute is 1.  Di2015NewLine/// </param>  Di2015NewLine/// <param name="group">  Di2015NewLine/// The relative priority group (e.g. Low or High) in which this SOAP extension runs when multiple SOAP extensions   Di2015NewLine/// are configured to run.  Di2015NewLine/// </param>  Di2015NewLine[ReflectionPermission(SecurityAction.Demand, Unrestricted = true)]  Di2015NewLinepublic static void RegisterSoapExtension(Type type, int priority, PriorityGroup group)  Di2015NewLine{  Di2015NewLine    if (!type.IsSubclassOf(typeof(SoapExtension)))  Di2015NewLine    {  Di2015NewLine        throw new ArgumentException("Type must be derived from SoapException.", "type");  Di2015NewLine    }  Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (priority < 1)  Di2015NewLine    {  Di2015NewLine        throw new ArgumentOutOfRangeException("priority", priority, "Priority must be greater or equal to 1.");  Di2015NewLine    }  Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // get the current web services settings...  Di2015NewLine    WebServicesSection wss = WebServicesSection.Current;  Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // set SoapExtensionTypes collection to read/write...  Di2015NewLine    FieldInfo readOnlyField = typeof(System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection).GetField("bReadOnly", BindingFlags.NonPublic | BindingFlags.Instance);  Di2015NewLine    readOnlyField.SetValue(wss.SoapExtensionTypes, false);  Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // inject SoapExtension...  Di2015NewLine    wss.SoapExtensionTypes.Add(new SoapExtensionTypeElement(type, priority, group));  Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // set SoapExtensionTypes collection back to readonly and clear modified flags...  Di2015NewLine    MethodInfo resetModifiedMethod = typeof(System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement).GetMethod("ResetModified", BindingFlags.NonPublic | BindingFlags.Instance);  Di2015NewLine    resetModifiedMethod.Invoke(wss.SoapExtensionTypes, null);  Di2015NewLine    MethodInfo setReadOnlyMethod = typeof(System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement).GetMethod("SetReadOnly", BindingFlags.NonPublic | BindingFlags.Instance);  Di2015NewLine    setReadOnlyMethod.Invoke(wss.SoapExtensionTypes, null);  Di2015NewLine} Di2015NewLine

8286761Di2015UniqueSeparator// internal class ArraySortHelper<T> : IArraySortHelper<T>Di2015NewLineinternal static void QuickSort(Di2015NewLine                         T[] keys, Di2015NewLine                         int left, Di2015NewLine                         int right, Di2015NewLine                         IComparer<T> comparer)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    doDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int a = left;Di2015NewLine        int b = right;Di2015NewLine        int num3 = a + ((b - a) >> 1);Di2015NewLine        ArraySortHelper<T>.SwapIfGreaterWithItems(keys, comparer, a, num3);Di2015NewLine        ArraySortHelper<T>.SwapIfGreaterWithItems(keys, comparer, a, b);Di2015NewLine        ArraySortHelper<T>.SwapIfGreaterWithItems(keys, comparer, num3, b);Di2015NewLine        T y = keys[num3];Di2015NewLine        doDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            while (comparer.Compare(keys[a], y) < 0)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                a++;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            while (comparer.Compare(y, keys[b]) < 0)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                b--;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            if (a > b)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                break;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            if (a < b)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                T local2 = keys[a];Di2015NewLine                keys[a] = keys[b];Di2015NewLine                keys[b] = local2;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            a++;Di2015NewLine            b--;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        while (a <= b);Di2015NewLine        if ((b - left) <= (right - a))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (left < b)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                ArraySortHelper<T>.QuickSort(keys, left, b, comparer);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            left = a;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (a < right)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                ArraySortHelper<T>.QuickSort(keys, a, right, comparer);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            right = b;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    while (left < right);Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLineprivate static void SwapIfGreaterWithItems(Di2015NewLine                                T[] keys, Di2015NewLine                                IComparer<T> comparer, Di2015NewLine                                int a, Di2015NewLine                                int b)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if ((a != b) && (comparer.Compare(keys[a], keys[b]) > 0))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        T local = keys[a];Di2015NewLine        keys[a] = keys[b];Di2015NewLine        keys[b] = local;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

Form1_Load(object sender, EventArgs e)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            //Resize the form and make it not user-resizableDi2015NewLine            this.Size = new Size(BORDER_WIDTH + 30, BORDER_HEIGHT + 50);Di2015NewLine            this.FormBorderStyle = System.Windows.Forms.FormBorderStyle.FixedSingle;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            //Create our "image"Di2015NewLine            pb = new PictureBox();Di2015NewLine            pb.Size = new Size(IMAGE_WIDTH, IMAGE_HEIGHT);Di2015NewLine            pb.Location = new Point(IMAGE_OFFSET, IMAGE_OFFSET);Di2015NewLine            pb.BackColor = Color.Red;Di2015NewLine            //Bind a handler to the mouse down eventDi2015NewLine            pb.MouseDown += new MouseEventHandler(this.pbMouseDown);Di2015NewLine            this.Controls.Add(pb);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            //Create our "border"Di2015NewLine            border = new PictureBox();Di2015NewLine            border.Size = new Size(BORDER_WIDTH, BORDER_HEIGHT);Di2015NewLine            border.Location = new Point(IMAGE_OFFSET, IMAGE_OFFSET);Di2015NewLine            border.BackColor = Color.Black;Di2015NewLine            this.Controls.Add(border);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        private void pbMouseDown(object sender, MouseEventArgs e)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            //Store the current x/y so that we can use them in calculations laterDi2015NewLine            offsetX = e.X;Di2015NewLine            offsetY = e.Y;Di2015NewLine            //When the mouse is down we want to remove the original mouse down handlerDi2015NewLine            pb.MouseDown -= new MouseEventHandler(this.pbMouseDown);Di2015NewLine            //Add to more handler looking for mouse up and mouse movementDi2015NewLine            pb.MouseUp += new MouseEventHandler(this.pbMouseUp);Di2015NewLine            pb.MouseMove += new MouseEventHandler(this.pbMouseMove);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        private void pbMouseUp(object sender, MouseEventArgs e)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            //When the mouse button is released, remove old handlers and add back the down eventDi2015NewLine            pb.MouseMove -= new MouseEventHandler(this.pbMouseMove);Di2015NewLine            pb.MouseUp -= new MouseEventHandler(this.pbMouseUp);Di2015NewLine            pb.MouseDown += new MouseEventHandler(this.pbMouseDown);Di2015NewLine            //Pop up a message, this is where something with iTextSharp would be doneDi2015NewLine            MessageBox.Show(String.Format("The top left of the image is at {0}x{1}", pb.Top - IMAGE_OFFSET, pb.Left - IMAGE_OFFSET));Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        private void pbMouseMove(object sender, MouseEventArgs e)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            //Calculate where to draw the "image" at nextDi2015NewLine            //First, calculate based on the current image's location, the offset that we stored ealier and the current mouse positionDi2015NewLine            int newLeft = e.X + pb.Left - offsetX;Di2015NewLine            int newTop = e.Y + pb.Top - offsetY;Di2015NewLine            //Next, make sure that we haven't gone over one of the boundaries of the "border"Di2015NewLine            if (newLeft < border.Left) newLeft = border.Left;Di2015NewLine            if (newTop < border.Top) newTop = border.Top;Di2015NewLine            if (newLeft + pb.Width > border.Right) newLeft = border.Right - pb.Width;Di2015NewLine            if (newTop + pb.Height > border.Bottom) newTop = border.Bottom - pb.Height;Di2015NewLine            //Finally, assign the new valueDi2015NewLine            pb.Left = newLeft;Di2015NewLine            pb.Top = newTop;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

        var keyProcessingTask = Task.Factory.StartNew(ProcessKeys);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            _stopEvent.Wait();Di2015NewLine            keyReaderTask.Wait();Di2015NewLine 8309612Di2015UniqueSeparator[Flags]Di2015NewLinepublic enum EdgesDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    None = 0,Di2015NewLine    Top = 1,Di2015NewLine    Bottom = 2,Di2015NewLine    Left = 4,Di2015NewLine    Right = 8,Di2015NewLine    Identical = Top + Bottom + Left + Right,Di2015NewLine    Inside = 16,Di2015NewLine    Covers = 32Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8309612Di2015UniqueSeparatorIntersect
8309612Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static Edges DetectEdgesCollision(Rectangle a, Rectangle b)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    var result = Edges.None;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (a == b) return Edges.Identical;Di2015NewLine    b.Intersect(a);Di2015NewLine    if (b.IsEmpty) return Edges.None;Di2015NewLine    if (a == b) return Edges.Covers;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (a.Top == b.Top && (a.Right >= b.Right && a.Left<=b.Left )) Di2015NewLine        result |= Edges.Top;Di2015NewLine    if (a.Bottom == b.Bottom && (a.Right >= b.Right && a.Left<=b.Left ))Di2015NewLine        result |= Edges.Bottom;Di2015NewLine    if (a.Left == b.Left && (a.Bottom >= b.Bottom && a.Top <= b.Top)) Di2015NewLine        result |= Edges.Left;Di2015NewLine    if (a.Right == b.Right && (a.Bottom >= b.Bottom && a.Top <= b.Top)) Di2015NewLine        result |= Edges.Right;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return result == Edges.None ? Edges.Inside : result;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8323047Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic void ExecuteCommandSync(object command)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine  tryDi2015NewLine  {Di2015NewLine    // create the ProcessStartInfo using "cmd" as the program to be run,Di2015NewLine    // and "/c " as the parameters.Di2015NewLine    // Incidentally, /c tells cmd that we want it to execute the command that follows,Di2015NewLine    // and then exit.Di2015NewLine    System.Diagnostics.ProcessStartInfo procStartInfo =Di2015NewLine      new System.Diagnostics.ProcessStartInfo("cmd", "/c " + command);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // The following commands are needed to redirect the standard output.Di2015NewLine    // This means that it will be redirected to the Process.StandardOutput StreamReader.Di2015NewLine    procStartInfo.RedirectStandardOutput = true;Di2015NewLine    procStartInfo.UseShellExecute = false;Di2015NewLine    // Do not create the black window.Di2015NewLine    procStartInfo.CreateNoWindow = true;Di2015NewLine    // Now we create a process, assign its ProcessStartInfo and start itDi2015NewLine    System.Diagnostics.Process proc = new System.Diagnostics.Process();Di2015NewLine    proc.StartInfo = procStartInfo;Di2015NewLine    proc.Start();Di2015NewLine    // Get the output into a stringDi2015NewLine    string result = proc.StandardOutput.ReadToEnd();Di2015NewLine    // Display the command output.Di2015NewLine    Console.WriteLine(result);Di2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLine  catch (Exception objException)Di2015NewLine  {Di2015NewLine    // Log the exceptionDi2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8327199Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static string Inc(string s){Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    System.Func<char,int> v = c => (int)((c<='9')?(c-'0'):(c-'A'+10));Di2015NewLine    System.Func<int,char> ch = d => (char)(d+((d<10)?'0':('A'-10)));    Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    s = s.ToUpper();    Di2015NewLine    var sb = new System.Text.StringBuilder(s.Length);Di2015NewLine    sb.Length = s.Length;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    int carry = 1;Di2015NewLine    for(int i=s.Length-1; i>=0; i--){Di2015NewLine        int x = v(s[i])+carry;    Di2015NewLine        carry = x/36;Di2015NewLine        sb[i] = ch(x%36);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    if (carry>0)Di2015NewLine        return ch(carry) + sb.ToString();Di2015NewLine    elseDi2015NewLine        return sb.ToString();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8331262Di2015UniqueSeparatorBruteForceRandomImplementation
8331262Di2015UniqueSeparatorRandom
8331262Di2015UniqueSeparator    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// This method uses a random based algorithm to create a two-dimensional array of [height, width] Di2015NewLine    /// with exactly locationsToFind locations set to 1. Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="height"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="width"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="locationsToFind"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <returns></returns>Di2015NewLine    public int[,] BruteForceRandomImplementation(int height, int width, int locationsToFind)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var random = new Random();Di2015NewLine        locationsToFind = LimitLocationsToFindToMaxLocations(height, width, locationsToFind);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Create our two-dimensional array.Di2015NewLine        var map = new int[height, width];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        int locationsFound = 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Randomly set positons to 1 untill we have set locationsToFind locations to 1. Di2015NewLine        while (locationsFound < locationsToFind)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            // Get a random Y location - limit the max value to our height - 1. Di2015NewLine            var randomY = random.Next(height);Di2015NewLine            // Get a random X location - limit the max value to our width - 1. Di2015NewLine            var randomX = random.Next(width);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            // Find another random location if this location is already set to 1. Di2015NewLine            if (map[randomY, randomX] == 1)Di2015NewLine                continue;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            // Otherwise set our location to 1 and increment the number of locations we've found.Di2015NewLine            map[randomY, randomX] = 1;Di2015NewLine            locationsFound += 1;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return map;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine
8331262Di2015UniqueSeparatorlocationsToFind
8331262Di2015UniqueSeparator    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// Limits the locationsToFind variable to the maximum available locations. This avoids attempting to Di2015NewLine    /// mark more locations than are available for our width and height. Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="height"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="width"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="locationsToFind"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <returns></returns>Di2015NewLine    public int LimitLocationsToFindToMaxLocations(int height, int width, int locationsToFind)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return Math.Min(locationsToFind, height * width);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine
8331262Di2015UniqueSeparatorShuffleImplementation
8331262Di2015UniqueSeparator    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// This method uses a shuffle based algorithm to create a two-dimensional array of [height, width] Di2015NewLine    /// with exactly locationsToFind locations set to 1. Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="height"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="width"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="locationsToFind"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <returns></returns>Di2015NewLine    public int[,] ShuffleImplementation(int height, int width, int locationsToFind)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        locationsToFind = LimitLocationsToFindToMaxLocations(height, width, locationsToFind);Di2015NewLine        // Create a 1 dimensional array large enough to contain all our values. Di2015NewLine        var array = new int[height * width];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Set locationToFind locations to 1. Di2015NewLine        for (int location = 0; location < locationsToFind; location++)Di2015NewLine            array[location] = 1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Shuffle our array.Di2015NewLine        Shuffle(array);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Now let's create our two-dimensional array.Di2015NewLine        var map = new int[height, width];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        int index = 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Expand our one-dimensional array into a two-dimensional one. Di2015NewLine        for (int y = 0; y < height; y++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            for (int x = 0; x < width; x++)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                map[y, x] = array[index];Di2015NewLine                index++;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return map;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// Shuffles a one-dimensional array using the Fisher-Yates shuffle. Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <typeparam name="T"></typeparam>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="arr"></param>Di2015NewLine    public static void Shuffle<T>(T[] array)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var random = new Random();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        for (int i = array.Length - 1; i > 0; i--)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            int n = random.Next(i + 1);Di2015NewLine            Swap(ref array[i], ref array[n]);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// Swaps two values around. Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <typeparam name="T"></typeparam>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="valueA"></param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="valueB"></param>Di2015NewLine    public static void Swap<T>(ref T valueA, ref T valueB)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        T tempValue = valueA;Di2015NewLine        valueA = valueB;Di2015NewLine        valueB = tempValue;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine
8331262Di2015UniqueSeparatorvar map = BruteForceRandomImplementation(7, 3, 5);Di2015NewLine
8331262Di2015UniqueSeparatorvar map = ShuffleImplementation(7, 3, 5);Di2015NewLine

8349767Di2015UniqueSeparatorList<>.Sort
8349767Di2015UniqueSeparator    private static Random rnd = new Random();Di2015NewLine    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// Chooses one of the items at random.Di2015NewLine    /// Di2015NewLine    /// Returns default if there are no items.Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    public static T RandomOrDefault<T>(this IEnumerable<T> source)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // We need the count:Di2015NewLine        var buffer = source as ICollection<T> ?? source.ToList(); // (iterate only once)Di2015NewLine        var itemCount = buffer.Count;Di2015NewLine        if (itemCount == 0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return default(T);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var index = rnd.Next(itemCount);Di2015NewLine        return buffer.ElementAt(index);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// Randomizes the order of the elements of a sequence. Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    public static IEnumerable<T> Randomize<T>(this IEnumerable<T> source)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // This code is an implementation of the FisherYates shuffle.Di2015NewLine        // The code was obtained from:Di2015NewLine        // http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1287567/c-is-using-random-and-orderby-a-good-shuffle-algorithm/1665080#1665080Di2015NewLine        T[] elements = source.ToArray();Di2015NewLine        // Note i > 0 to avoid final pointless iterationDi2015NewLine        for (int i = elements.Length - 1; i > 0; i--)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            // Swap element "i" with a random earlier element it (or itself)Di2015NewLine            int swapIndex = rnd.Next(i + 1);Di2015NewLine            yield return elements[swapIndex];Di2015NewLine            elements[swapIndex] = elements[i];Di2015NewLine            // we don't actually perform the swap; we can forget about theDi2015NewLine            // swapped element because we already returned it.Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // there is one item remaining that was not returned - we return it nowDi2015NewLine        yield return elements[0];Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

8353245Di2015UniqueSeparatorusing System;Di2015NewLineusing System.Collections.Generic;Di2015NewLineusing System.IO;Di2015NewLineusing System.Linq;Di2015NewLineusing System.Text;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinenamespace StreamTestDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    public class EnumeratorStream : StreamDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        private readonly IEnumerator<string> source;Di2015NewLine        private readonly Encoding encoding;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public Encoding Encoding { get { return encoding; } }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        private byte[] current = new byte[0];Di2015NewLine        private int currentPos = 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public EnumeratorStream(IEnumerable<string> source, Encoding encoding)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (source == null) throw new ArgumentNullException("source");Di2015NewLine            if (encoding == null) encoding = Encoding.Default;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            this.source = source.GetEnumerator();Di2015NewLine            this.encoding = encoding;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        private bool MoveNext()Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            while (source.MoveNext())Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                if (source.Current.Length > 0)Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    current = encoding.GetBytes(source.Current);Di2015NewLine                    currentPos = 0;Di2015NewLine                    return true;Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            current = new byte[0];Di2015NewLine            currentPos = 0;Di2015NewLine            return false;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        #region Overrides of StreamDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public override bool CanRead { get { return true; Di2015NewLine        static DataTable GetTreeTable()Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            DataTable table = new DataTable();Di2015NewLine            table.Columns.Add("Id", typeof(int));Di2015NewLine            table.Columns.Add("Description", typeof(string));Di2015NewLine            table.Columns.Add("Url", typeof(string));Di2015NewLine            table.Columns.Add("ParentId", typeof(int));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            table.Rows.Add(1, "TopMenu1", "/foo.html", 0);Di2015NewLine            table.Rows.Add(2, "SubMenu1.1", "/baz.html", 1);Di2015NewLine            table.Rows.Add(3, "SubMenu1.2", "/barry.html", 1);Di2015NewLine            table.Rows.Add(4, "SubMenu1.2.1", "/skeet.html", 3);Di2015NewLine            table.Rows.Add(5, "TopMenu2", "/bar.html", 0);Di2015NewLine            table.Rows.Add(6, "TopMenu3", "/bar.html", 0);Di2015NewLine            table.Rows.Add(7, "SubMenu3.1", "/ack.html", 6);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            return table;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // See e.g. http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2654627/most-efficient-way-of-creating-tree-from-adjacency-listDi2015NewLine        // Assuming table is ordered.Di2015NewLine        static MenuNode ConvertTableToTree(DataTable table)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            var map = new Dictionary<int, MenuNode>();Di2015NewLine            map[0] = new MenuNode() { Id = 0 }; // root nodeDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            foreach (DataRow row in table.Rows)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                int nodeId = int.Parse(row["Id"].ToString());Di2015NewLine                int parentId = int.Parse(row["ParentId"].ToString());Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                MenuNode newNode = MenuNodeFromDataRow(row);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                map[parentId].Children.Add(newNode);Di2015NewLine                map[nodeId] = newNode;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            return map[0]; // root nodeDi2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        static MenuNode MenuNodeFromDataRow(DataRow row)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            int nodeId = int.Parse(row["Id"].ToString());Di2015NewLine            int parentId = int.Parse(row["ParentId"].ToString());Di2015NewLine            string description = row["Description"].ToString();Di2015NewLine            string url = row["Url"].ToString();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            return new MenuNode() { Id=nodeId, ParentId=parentId, Description=description, Url=url };Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8383207Di2015UniqueSeparatorstring Match(string str)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if( str.Length == 0 || str[0] == ')' ) Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return str;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    if( str[0] == '(' )Di2015NewLine    {           Di2015NewLine        string closer = Match(str.Substring(1));Di2015NewLine        // The original code has a hidden check for termination here!Di2015NewLine        // If *closer was '\\0', it would not enter the ifDi2015NewLine        // Let's keep that and avoid IndexOutOfRange.Di2015NewLine        if( closer.Length > 0 && closer[0] == ')' )Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine                return Match(closer.Substring(1));Di2015NewLine        }           Di2015NewLine        // The original just restored the pointer to its initial state.Di2015NewLine        // Since C# strings are immutable, we can just return the original string.Di2015NewLine        return str;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return match(str.Substring(1));Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
8383207Di2015UniqueSeparatorint Match(string str, int i)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if( str.Length == i || str[i] == ')' ) Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return i;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    if( str[i] == '(' )Di2015NewLine    {           Di2015NewLine        int closerIdx = Match(str, i+1);Di2015NewLine        if( str.Length > closerIdx && str[closerIdx] == ')' )Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine                return Match(str, closerIdx+1);Di2015NewLine        }           Di2015NewLine        return i;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return Match(str, i+1);Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8393780Di2015UniqueSeparator  private static final HashSet<ArrayList<Double>> lists = Di2015NewLine       new HashSet<ArrayList<Double>>(); // all of the combinations generatedDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine  private static final double[] elements = {10, 7, 3, 1};Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine  public static void main(String[] args) {Di2015NewLine    combine(20, new ArrayList<Double>());Di2015NewLine    for (ArrayList<Double> set : lists) {Di2015NewLine      System.out.println(set);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine  private static void combine(final double limit, ArrayList<Double> stack) {Di2015NewLine    // iterates through the elements that fit in the thresholdDi2015NewLine    for (double item : elements) {Di2015NewLine      if (item < limit) {Di2015NewLine        final ArrayList<Double> nextStack = new ArrayList<Double>(stack);Di2015NewLine        nextStack.add(item);Di2015NewLine        // a sort is necessary to let the HashSet de-dup properlyDi2015NewLine        Collections.sort(nextStack);Di2015NewLine        lists.add(nextStack);Di2015NewLine        combine(limit - item, nextStack);Di2015NewLine      }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLine
8393780Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic void Main(string[] args)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Run();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static public void Run()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Combine(20, new List<Double>());Di2015NewLine        foreach (List<Double> set in lists)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            Debug.Print(set.ToString());Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    private static HashSet<List<Double>> lists =Di2015NewLine        new HashSet<List<Double>>(); // all of the combinations generatedDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private static double[] elements = { 10, 7, 3, 1 };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private static void Combine(double limit, List<Double> stack)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // iterates through the elements that fit in the thresholdDi2015NewLine        foreach (double item in elements)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (item < limit)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                List<Double> nextStack = new List<Double>(stack);Di2015NewLine                nextStack.Add(item);Di2015NewLine                // a sort is necessary to let the HashSet de-dup properlyDi2015NewLine                nextStack.Sort();Di2015NewLine                lists.Add(nextStack);Di2015NewLine                Combine(limit - item, nextStack);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

8400351Di2015UniqueSeparatorIt should be noted each of the groups of allowed child elements of the <schema> element has a corresponding property in the XmlSchema class except one, <annotation> elements. This has led some to believe that one cannot obtain annotations from the XmlSchema class, which is not the case. Annotations can be retrieved from the Items property of the XmlSchema class. The following code sample shows how to print the contents of the annotation in the books.xsd schema.

8405599Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate void OpenXmlFileHandling(String fileName)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        using (SpreadsheetDocument document = SpreadsheetDocument.Open(fileName, true))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            //some sample valuesDi2015NewLine            String definedName = "Worksheet3";Di2015NewLine            String topLeft = "$A$3";Di2015NewLine            String bottomRight = "$D$7";Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            WorkbookPart wbPart = document.WorkbookPart;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            var definedNames = wbPart.Workbook.Descendants<DefinedNames>().FirstOrDefault();Di2015NewLine            var namesCollection = definedNames.Descendants<DefinedName>().Where(m => m.Text.StartsWith(definedName));Di2015NewLine            DefinedName name = namesCollection != null ? namesCollection.First() : null;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            UInt32Value locSheetId;Di2015NewLine            //we assume that name is not null, because print range for this worksheet was defined in the source template fileDi2015NewLine            //if name was null, we should probably just assign to locSheetId a number definedNames.Count() + 1 and not remove the name nodeDi2015NewLine            locSheetId = name.LocalSheetId;Di2015NewLine            name.Remove();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            wbPart.Workbook.Save();Di2015NewLine            name = new DefinedName() { Name = "_xlnm.Print_Area", LocalSheetId = locSheetId, Text = String.Format("{0}!{1}:{2}", definedName, topLeft, bottomRight) };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            definedNames.Append(name);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            wbPart.Workbook.Save();Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

8416167Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static string Split(this string target, Func<char, char, bool> shouldSplit, string splitFiller = " ")Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if (target == null)Di2015NewLine        throw new ArgumentNullException("target");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (shouldSplit == null)Di2015NewLine        throw new ArgumentNullException("shouldSplit");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (String.IsNullOrEmpty(splitFiller))Di2015NewLine        throw new ArgumentNullException("splitFiller");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    int targetLength = target.Length;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // We know the resulting string is going to be atleast the length of targetDi2015NewLine    StringBuilder result = new StringBuilder(targetLength);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    result.Append(target[0]);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Loop from the second character to the last character.Di2015NewLine    for (int i = 1; i < targetLength; ++i)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        char firstChar = target[i - 1];Di2015NewLine        char secondChar = target[i];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (shouldSplit(firstChar, secondChar))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            // If a split should be performed add in the fillerDi2015NewLine            result.Append(splitFiller);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        result.Append(secondChar);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return result.ToString();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8421356Di2015UniqueSeparatorprotected Expression<Func<TElement, bool>> BuildContainsExpression<TElement, TValue>(Expression<Func<TElement, TValue>> valueSelector, IEnumerable<TValue> values)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine            if (null == valueSelector) { throw new ArgumentNullException("valueSelector"); }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            if (null == values) { throw new ArgumentNullException("values"); }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            ParameterExpression p = valueSelector.Parameters.Single();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            if (!values.Any())Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                return e => false;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            var equals = values.Select(value => (Expression)Expression.Equal(valueSelector.Body, Expression.Constant(value, typeof(TValue))));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            var body = equals.Aggregate<Expression>((accumulate, equal) => Expression.Or(accumulate, equal));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            return Expression.Lambda<Func<TElement, bool>>(body, p);Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8423189Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic class DoubleFormatter : IFormatProvider, ICustomFormatter Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    // Implementation of IFormatProvider:Di2015NewLine    public object GetFormat(Type t) {Di2015NewLine        if (t == typeof(ICustomFormatter)) {Di2015NewLine            return this;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return null;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    // Implementation of ICustomFormatter:Di2015NewLine    public string Format(string format, object arg, IFormatProvider provider) {Di2015NewLine        // Search for the custom "EE" format specifier:Di2015NewLine        if (format == null || !format.StartsWith("EE")) return null;Di2015NewLine        format = format.Substring(2); // Trim "EE"Di2015NewLine        // Determine how many digits before we cutoff:Di2015NewLine        int digits;Di2015NewLine        if (!int.TryParse(format, out digits)) {Di2015NewLine            throw new FormatException("Format must contain digits");Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Get the value: (note, this will work for any numeric type)Di2015NewLine        var value = Convert.ToDouble(arg);Di2015NewLine        // Convert to string without using Exponential format:Di2015NewLine        var output = value.ToString("0."+(new string('#',digits)), provider);Di2015NewLine        // Determine how many digits are showing: (this part isn't culture-compatible)Di2015NewLine        var length = output.Length - output.IndexOf(".");Di2015NewLine        if (length <= digits) {Di2015NewLine            return output;Di2015NewLine        } else {Di2015NewLine            return value.ToString("E"+format, provider);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8424148Di2015UniqueSeparatorfunction decryptAES128CBC($content,$iv, $key) {Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // AES is Rijndael-128Di2015NewLine    $rijndael = 'rijndael-128';Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // key size is 128 bit = 16 bytesDi2015NewLine    $ks = 16;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // CBC mode, not OFBDi2015NewLine    $cp = mcrypt_module_open($rijndael, '', 'cbc', '');Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // pad key and IV by zeros (this is not a good idea)Di2015NewLine    $key = str_pad($key, $ks, "\\0");Di2015NewLine    $iv = str_pad($key, $iv, "\\0");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // initialize the decryptor with key and IVDi2015NewLine    mcrypt_generic_init($cp, $key, $iv);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // the actual workDi2015NewLine    $decrypted = mdecrypt_generic($cp, $content);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // clean upDi2015NewLine    mcrypt_generic_deinit($cp);Di2015NewLine    mcrypt_module_close($cp);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // remove padding, see belowDi2015NewLine    return unpad($decrypted);Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8450271Di2015UniqueSeparator/// <summary>Di2015NewLine/// Rotates the bits in an array of bytes to the left.Di2015NewLine/// </summary>Di2015NewLine/// <param name="bytes">The byte array to rotate.</param>Di2015NewLinepublic static void RotateLeft(byte[] bytes)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    bool carryFlag = ShiftLeft(bytes);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (carryFlag == true)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        bytes[bytes.Length - 1] = (byte)(bytes[bytes.Length - 1] | 0x01);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine/// <summary>Di2015NewLine/// Rotates the bits in an array of bytes to the right.Di2015NewLine/// </summary>Di2015NewLine/// <param name="bytes">The byte array to rotate.</param>Di2015NewLinepublic static void RotateRight(byte[] bytes)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    bool carryFlag = ShiftRight(bytes);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (carryFlag == true)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        bytes[0] = (byte)(bytes[0] | 0x80);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine/// <summary>Di2015NewLine/// Shifts the bits in an array of bytes to the left.Di2015NewLine/// </summary>Di2015NewLine/// <param name="bytes">The byte array to shift.</param>Di2015NewLinepublic static bool ShiftLeft(byte[] bytes)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    bool leftMostCarryFlag = false;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Iterate through the elements of the array from left to right.Di2015NewLine    for (int index = 0; index < bytes.Length; index++)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // If the leftmost bit of the current byte is 1 then we have a carry.Di2015NewLine        bool carryFlag = (bytes[index] & 0x80) > 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (index > 0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (carryFlag == true)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                // Apply the carry to the rightmost bit of the current bytes neighbor to the left.Di2015NewLine                bytes[index - 1] = (byte)(bytes[index - 1] | 0x01);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            leftMostCarryFlag = carryFlag;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        bytes[index] = (byte)(bytes[index] << 1);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return leftMostCarryFlag;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine/// <summary>Di2015NewLine/// Shifts the bits in an array of bytes to the right.Di2015NewLine/// </summary>Di2015NewLine/// <param name="bytes">The byte array to shift.</param>Di2015NewLinepublic static bool ShiftRight(byte[] bytes) Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    bool rightMostCarryFlag = false;Di2015NewLine    int rightEnd = bytes.Length - 1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Iterate through the elements of the array right to left.Di2015NewLine    for (int index = rightEnd; index >= 0; index--)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // If the rightmost bit of the current byte is 1 then we have a carry.Di2015NewLine        bool carryFlag = (bytes[index] & 0x01) > 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (index < rightEnd)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (carryFlag == true)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                // Apply the carry to the leftmost bit of the current bytes neighbor to the right.Di2015NewLine                bytes[index + 1] = (byte)(bytes[index + 1] | 0x80);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            rightMostCarryFlag = carryFlag;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        bytes[index] = (byte)(bytes[index] >> 1);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return rightMostCarryFlag;Di2015NewLine} Di2015NewLine

8453731Di2015UniqueSeparatordef permutations_of( seq ):Di2015NewLine    yield seqDi2015NewLine    seqlen = len(seq)Di2015NewLine    while True:Di2015NewLine        j = seqlen - 2Di2015NewLine        while j >= 0 and seq[j] >= seq[j+1]:Di2015NewLine            j -= 1Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if j < 0: breakDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        i= seqlen - 1Di2015NewLine        while i > j and seq[i] < seq[j]:Di2015NewLine            i -= 1Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        seq[j],seq[i] = seq[i],seq[j]Di2015NewLine        seq[j+1:] = seq[-1:j:-1]Di2015NewLine        yield seqDi2015NewLine

8458496Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic decimal CustomParseDecimal(string input) {Di2015NewLine    long n = 0;Di2015NewLine    int decimalPosition = input.Length;Di2015NewLine    for (int k = 0; k < input.Length; k++) {Di2015NewLine        char c = input[k];Di2015NewLine        if (c == '.')Di2015NewLine            decimalPosition = k + 1;Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine            n = (n * 10) + (int)(c - '0');Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    return new decimal((int)n, (int)(n >> 32), 0, false, (byte)(input.Length - decimalPosition));Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

HttpApplication, ByVal cacheKey As String)Di2015NewLine            'Mark the current request by adding QueryString parameter.Di2015NewLine            Dim request As HttpWebRequest = CType(WebRequest.Create((app.Context.Request.Url.OriginalString + "&" + MARK + "=1")), HttpWebRequest)Di2015NewLine            request.Credentials = CredentialCache.DefaultNetworkCredentialsDi2015NewLine            Using response As HttpWebResponse = CType(request.GetResponse, HttpWebResponse)Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                If (True) ThenDi2015NewLine                    ' We getting the response stream, that raise again the 'BeginRequest' event (that why we marked the request)Di2015NewLine                    Dim responseStream As javascript or css content.Di2015NewLine                    ' We compress only WebResources that are Javascript or css file.Di2015NewLine                    ' The problem is, that we can know the content type only after we got the response. TODO: find a better solutionDi2015NewLine                    ' for non CSS or JS contentDi2015NewLine                    If Not IsContentSupported(contentType) ThenDi2015NewLine compressionDi2015NewLine                        StreamCopy(responseStream, app.Response.OutputStream)Di2015NewLine                        responseStream.Dispose()Di2015NewLine so we can convert it into byte[] easly.Di2015NewLine                    Dim dataStream As New MemoryStream()Di2015NewLine                    StreamCopy(responseStream, dataStream)Di2015NewLine                    responseStream.Dispose()Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                    ' Convert the response into byte[]Di2015NewLine                    Dim data As Byte() = memstream As MemoryStream = New MemoryStreamDi2015NewLine                        Dim compress As Stream = NothingDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                        ' Choose the compression type and make the compressionDi2015NewLine                        If IsGzipEncodingSupported() ThenDi2015NewLine                            compress = New GZipStream(memstream, CompressionMode.Compress)Di2015NewLine                            encodingType = GZIPDi2015NewLine                        ElseDi2015NewLine                            If IsDeflateEncodingSupported()                      End IfDi2015NewLine                        End IfDi2015NewLine                        compress.Write(data, 0, data.Length)Di2015NewLine    case '':Di2015NewLine                case '':Di2015NewLine                case '':Di2015NewLine                case '':Di2015NewLine                case '':Di2015NewLine                case '':Di2015NewLine                    f[++position] = 'z';Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine                case '\\x00a0': // no-break spaceDi2015NewLine                case '\\x2000': // other spacesDi2015NewLine                case '\\x2001':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x2002':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x2003':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x2004':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x2005':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x2006':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x2007':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x2008':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x2009':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x200a':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x200b':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x200c':Di2015NewLine                case '\\x200d':Di2015NewLine                    if (position > -1 && f[position] != '-') f[++position] = '-';Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        else if ((s[index] > '\\x002f' && s[index] < '\\x003a') || (s[index] > '\\x0060' && s[index] < '\\x007b'))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            f[++position] = s[index];Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        else if ((s[index] > '\\x0040' && s[index] < '\\x005b'))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            f[++position] = (char)(s[index] | ' ');Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            switch (s[index])Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                case '#':Di2015NewLine                    if (position > 0 && (f[position] == 'c' || f[position] == 'j' || f[position] == 'f'))Di2015NewLine                    {Di2015NewLine                        f[++position] = 's';Di2015NewLine                        f[++position] = 'h';Di2015NewLine                        f[++position] = 'a';Di2015NewLine                        f[++position] = 'r';Di2015NewLine                        f[++position] = 'p';Di2015NewLine                    }Di2015NewLine                    else if (index + 1 < len && ((s[index + 1] >= '0') && (s[index + 1] <= '9')))Di2015NewLine                    {Di2015NewLine                        f[++position] = 'n';Di2015NewLine                        f[++position] = 'o';Di2015NewLine                    }Di2015NewLine                    else if (position > -1 && f[position] != '-') f[++position] = '-';Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine                case '+':Di2015NewLine                    f[++position] = 'p';Di2015NewLine                    f[++position] = 'l';Di2015NewLine                    f[++position] = 'u';Di2015NewLine                    f[++position] = 's';Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine                case '.':Di2015NewLine                    //f[++position] = 'd';Di2015NewLine                    //f[++position] = 'o';Di2015NewLine                    //f[++position] = 't';Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine                case '-':Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine                default:Di2015NewLine                    if (position > -1 && f[position] != '-') f[++position] = '-';Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        if (f[position] == '-' && ws < position)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            for (var i = ws; i < position; i++) w.Append(f[i]);Di2015NewLine            word = w.ToString();Di2015NewLine            if (dict.ContainsKey(word)) dict[word] += 1;Di2015NewLine            else dict.Add(word, 1);Di2015NewLine            w = new StringBuilder(50);Di2015NewLine            ws = position + 1;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    if (f[position] == '-') position--;Di2015NewLine    return f.ToString(0, position + 1);Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

8468520Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic void Main(string[] args)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    HttpListener listener = new HttpListener();Di2015NewLine    listener.Prefixes.Add("http://localhost:8080/ListenerTest/");Di2015NewLine    listener.Start();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    HttpListenerContext context = context.Response.StatusCode = 200;Di2015NewLine    context.Response.ContentType = "text/html";Di2015NewLine    using (StreamWriter writer = new StreamWriter(context.Response.OutputStream, Encoding.UTF8))Di2015NewLine        writer.WriteLine("File Uploaded");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    context.Response.Close();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    listener.Stop();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineprivate static String GetBoundary(String ctype)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    return "--" + ctype.Split(';')[1].Split('=')[1];Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineprivate static void SaveFile(Encoding enc, String boundary, Stream input)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    Byte[] boundaryBytes = enc.GetBytes(boundary);Di2015NewLine    Int32 boundaryLen = boundaryBytes.Length;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    using (FileStream output = new FileStream("data", FileMode.Create, FileAccess.Write))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Byte[] buffer = new Byte[1024];Di2015NewLine        Int32 len = input.Read(buffer, 0, 1024);Di2015NewLine        Int32 startPos = -1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Find start boundaryDi2015NewLine        while (true)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (len == 0)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                throw new Exception("Start Boundaray Not Found");Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            startPos = IndexOf(buffer, len, boundaryBytes);Di2015NewLine            if (startPos >= 0)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                break;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                Array.Copy(buffer, len - boundaryLen, buffer, 0, boundaryLen);Di2015NewLine                len = input.Read(buffer, boundaryLen, 1024 - boundaryLen);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Skip four lines (Boundary, Content-Disposition, Content-Type, and a blank)Di2015NewLine        for (Int32 i = 0; i < 4; i++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            while (true)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                if (len == 0)Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    throw new Exception("Preamble not Found.");Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                startPos = Array.IndexOf(buffer, enc.GetBytes("\\n")[0], startPos);Di2015NewLine                if (startPos >= 0)Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    startPos++;Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine                elseDi2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    len = input.Read(buffer, 0, 1024);Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        Array.Copy(buffer, startPos, buffer, 0, len - startPos);Di2015NewLine        len = len - startPos;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        while (true)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            Int32 endPos = IndexOf(buffer, len, boundaryBytes);Di2015NewLine            if (endPos >= 0)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                if (endPos > 0) output.Write(buffer, 0, endPos);Di2015NewLine                break;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            else if (len <= boundaryLen)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                throw new Exception("End Boundaray Not Found");Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                output.Write(buffer, 0, len - boundaryLen);Di2015NewLine                Array.Copy(buffer, len - boundaryLen, buffer, 0, boundaryLen);Di2015NewLine                len = input.Read(buffer, boundaryLen, 1024 - boundaryLen) + boundaryLen;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineprivate static Int32 IndexOf(Byte[] buffer, Int32 len, Byte[] boundaryBytes)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    for (Int32 i = 0; i <= len - boundaryBytes.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Boolean match = true;Di2015NewLine        for (Int32 j = 0; j < boundaryBytes.Length && match; j++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            match = buffer[i + j] == boundaryBytes[j];Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (match)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return i;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return -1;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
